1
00:00:05,607 --> 00:00:08,303
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,376 --> 00:00:12,244
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,313 --> 00:00:16,306
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,651 --> 00:00:19,142
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:23,281
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,358 --> 00:00:27,317
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,797 --> 00:00:33,530
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,235 --> 00:00:37,204
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,641 --> 00:00:41,734
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,477 --> 00:00:43,774
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,112 --> 00:00:46,672
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,722 --> 00:01:00,092
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,295 --> 00:01:01,455
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,529 --> 00:01:05,329
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,667 --> 00:01:10,866
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,139 --> 00:01:12,470
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:13,939
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,008 --> 00:01:20,277
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:45,127 --> 00:01:48,221
<i>Where is...this place...?</i>

20
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:58,672
<i>Who is it?</i>

21
00:02:02,978 --> 00:02:05,947
<i>Me...</i>
<i>from long ago?</i>

22
00:02:07,416 --> 00:02:11,011
<i>Father and mother didn't need to die!</i>

23
00:02:18,627 --> 00:02:19,992
<i>Everyone was killed.</i>

24
00:02:22,031 --> 00:02:24,363
<i>I had no power so...</i>

25
00:02:25,968 --> 00:02:28,095
<i>the clan vanished.</i>

26
00:02:41,217 --> 00:02:46,314
<i>Battle Formation. Ino Shika Cho!</i>

27
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:57,758
Ino... Why?

28
00:02:58,934 --> 00:03:02,927
I can't let you upstage me
in front of Sasuke!

29
00:03:03,606 --> 00:03:05,301
Squirming again...

30
00:03:06,375 --> 00:03:09,902
The Leaf Village worms wandered in.

31
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:13,371
What are the two of you thinking?!

32
00:03:13,816 --> 00:03:15,647
They're bad news!

33
00:03:15,718 --> 00:03:17,777
It's a pain, but it can't be helped!

34
00:03:17,953 --> 00:03:21,480
Ino steps out and
we men should run?

35
00:03:23,659 --> 00:03:25,718
Sorry to get you involved.

36
00:03:25,928 --> 00:03:27,987
But anyway we're
a Three-Man Squad, after all.

37
00:03:28,063 --> 00:03:29,997
We're all in this together, aren't we?

38
00:03:30,232 --> 00:03:32,325
Well, we'll see.

39
00:03:32,935 --> 00:03:35,836
No! I don't want to die yet!

40
00:03:35,905 --> 00:03:37,202
Let go of my scarf!

41
00:03:37,273 --> 00:03:39,503
You're annoying! Quit wiggling!

42
00:03:41,043 --> 00:03:44,877
It's okay for you to drop out, fatso.

43
00:03:46,348 --> 00:03:49,181
What did that guy just say?

44
00:03:49,885 --> 00:03:52,718
I... didn't quite catch it.

45
00:03:52,888 --> 00:03:53,684
Huh?!

46
00:03:54,490 --> 00:03:56,890
<i>That word is taboo to Choji.</i>

47
00:03:57,526 --> 00:03:59,517
Try saying it again...

48
00:03:59,962 --> 00:04:04,092
I said if you have a problem,
pull out, fatso.

49
00:04:04,166 --> 00:04:07,499
<i>Fatso...fatso...fatso...fatso... fatso</i>

50
00:04:10,973 --> 00:04:14,500
I'm not fat, I'm just big boned!
Blast it!

51
00:04:19,381 --> 00:04:21,508
Hurraaaay for Big-Boned!

52
00:04:23,218 --> 00:04:24,845
<i>W-Wow...</i>

53
00:04:25,421 --> 00:04:27,912
All right! You understand this, right?!

54
00:04:28,157 --> 00:04:30,819
This is a battle between Leaf and Sound!

55
00:04:32,895 --> 00:04:34,294
<i>Lucky! He's lost it!</i>

56
00:04:34,964 --> 00:04:37,831
No way, this looks like it's going
to be a pain in the butt.

57
00:04:38,667 --> 00:04:40,430
That's my line.

58
00:04:41,537 --> 00:04:44,870
<i>I was told to get Sasuke</i>
<i>by the end of the test...</i>

59
00:04:47,209 --> 00:04:48,403
Sasuke...

60
00:04:48,544 --> 00:04:49,340
Sakura...

61
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:54,408
The two behind...
take care of them.

62
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:58,979
Okay!

63
00:04:59,388 --> 00:05:02,448
Well then, Team Ino,
let's go full throttle!

64
00:05:02,858 --> 00:05:03,790
Right!

65
00:05:04,493 --> 00:05:06,051
Formation Ino!

66
00:05:06,128 --> 00:05:07,527
- Shika!
- Cho!

67
00:05:09,531 --> 00:05:11,590
I'm counting on you, Choji

68
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,824
Okay!

69
00:05:13,068 --> 00:05:14,000
Expansion Jutsu!

70
00:05:15,437 --> 00:05:17,564
Next, Leaf Style Taijutsu!

71
00:05:23,712 --> 00:05:25,373
Human Boulder!

72
00:05:28,317 --> 00:05:29,614
What is this Jutsu?

73
00:05:29,752 --> 00:05:31,947
Isn't it just a fat guy rolling?

74
00:05:32,688 --> 00:05:34,315
Slicing Sound Wave!

75
00:05:46,468 --> 00:05:47,400
You!

76
00:05:55,811 --> 00:05:56,675
He jumped?!

77
00:05:58,514 --> 00:06:00,038
<i>The air pressure of</i>
<i>Slicing Sound Wave</i>

78
00:06:00,115 --> 00:06:02,015
<i>is less than effective</i>
<i>against that rotation.</i>

79
00:06:02,284 --> 00:06:06,311
<i>Even if I do the Super Sound Wave,</i>
<i>if I'm touched by something like that</i>

80
00:06:06,388 --> 00:06:08,413
<i>the bones in my arms will be crushed!</i>

81
00:06:14,596 --> 00:06:15,585
<i>Think I'll let you?!</i>

82
00:06:15,664 --> 00:06:18,189
<i>You're the most annoying so...</i>

83
00:06:18,634 --> 00:06:19,566
Ninja Art!

84
00:06:19,835 --> 00:06:21,166
Shadow Possession Jutsu!

85
00:06:25,874 --> 00:06:27,102
<i>My body!</i>

86
00:06:27,176 --> 00:06:27,870
Huh?!

87
00:06:38,987 --> 00:06:39,681
Dosu?!

88
00:06:39,755 --> 00:06:41,552
What are you doing at a time like this?!

89
00:06:47,229 --> 00:06:49,060
Shadow Paralysis Jutsu?

90
00:06:50,532 --> 00:06:52,932
Ino, next it's just the ladies.

91
00:06:53,001 --> 00:06:56,960
Okay, Shikamaru, look after my body.

92
00:06:57,106 --> 00:06:58,004
Gotcha!

93
00:06:58,073 --> 00:06:58,801
Huh?

94
00:06:59,408 --> 00:07:01,774
Ninja Art, Mind Transfer Jutsu!

95
00:07:12,421 --> 00:07:13,149
Shoot!

96
00:07:14,923 --> 00:07:15,787
Kin!

97
00:07:19,161 --> 00:07:20,321
What happened?

98
00:07:25,601 --> 00:07:27,000
This... is the end of it.

99
00:07:28,303 --> 00:07:29,235
You guys!

100
00:07:29,304 --> 00:07:32,705
If you make one move,
this girl named Kin is dead meat!

101
00:07:33,041 --> 00:07:34,804
If you don't want this
to end right here,

102
00:07:34,877 --> 00:07:37,243
leave your scroll and walk away!

103
00:07:37,746 --> 00:07:40,806
Once you've gone far enough that
I can't feel your Chakras,

104
00:07:40,883 --> 00:07:43,078
I'll release this girl!

105
00:07:44,019 --> 00:07:46,510
<i>These guys...</i>
<i>What are they grinning about?</i>

106
00:07:47,422 --> 00:07:49,151
- Choji!
- Yeah!

107
00:07:49,458 --> 00:07:51,085
This isn't good! They won't...!

108
00:07:57,432 --> 00:07:58,330
Ino!

109
00:07:59,234 --> 00:08:01,828
Uggghh. I'm dizzy.

110
00:08:04,406 --> 00:08:08,809
W-What kind of person...
hurts their own comrades?

111
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,611
Careless.

112
00:08:13,048 --> 00:08:20,113
Our goal is not the scrolls or
to pass this test playing by the rules.

113
00:08:21,256 --> 00:08:22,154
What?

114
00:08:22,558 --> 00:08:23,957
It's Sasuke.

115
00:08:32,301 --> 00:08:33,325
Humph...

116
00:08:34,570 --> 00:08:35,969
<i>My Jutsu...</i>

117
00:08:36,271 --> 00:08:38,739
So your much precious
Shadow Paralysis Jutsu

118
00:08:38,807 --> 00:08:40,968
is limited to 5 minutes?

119
00:08:41,076 --> 00:08:44,273
It's not Shadow Paralysis.
It's Shadow Possession Jutsu.

120
00:08:45,314 --> 00:08:47,407
In addition, it seems that
this girl's Jutsu...

121
00:08:47,683 --> 00:08:53,019
seems to be a Jutsu to
take over the other's body.

122
00:08:53,522 --> 00:08:55,422
From the looks of the blood
she's spitting up,

123
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:59,153
if I kill Kin, that girl will die too...

124
00:08:59,528 --> 00:09:01,996
Are you going to do in...
your teammate?

125
00:09:02,898 --> 00:09:04,889
If I need to...

126
00:09:10,405 --> 00:09:11,872
This is no good.

127
00:09:12,174 --> 00:09:13,334
Shit...

128
00:09:14,243 --> 00:09:18,577
That's too bad...
you're just a step away.

129
00:09:18,981 --> 00:09:20,676
You're too easy going.

130
00:09:21,383 --> 00:09:23,442
Hmph, I don't like this at all.

131
00:09:23,652 --> 00:09:27,019
You minor Sound Ninjas...

132
00:09:27,322 --> 00:09:30,951
Bullying the second rate guys and
putting on airs like a winner.

133
00:09:31,326 --> 00:09:32,054
What?!

134
00:09:36,131 --> 00:09:38,565
They're Lee's teammates...

135
00:09:42,304 --> 00:09:43,100
Lee!

136
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,731
You goofed.

137
00:09:45,407 --> 00:09:49,434
Hah! Coming out of nowhere
like cockroaches...

138
00:09:50,312 --> 00:09:54,009
That kid with the bob lying over there
is on our team, but...

139
00:09:55,317 --> 00:09:56,909
But you messed with him, didn't you?!

140
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,619
<i>What's with his eyes?</i>

141
00:10:08,430 --> 00:10:11,331
It's like they see through everything...

142
00:10:12,234 --> 00:10:15,465
If you're gonna continue,
I'll fight with full strength!

143
00:10:17,072 --> 00:10:17,595
Huh?

144
00:10:18,373 --> 00:10:19,931
What's wrong? Neji...

145
00:10:20,676 --> 00:10:22,041
<i>This Chakra...</i>

146
00:10:23,912 --> 00:10:28,008
If you don't like me,
don't play cool, come down here.

147
00:10:28,517 --> 00:10:32,248
No. Evidently, there's no need for that.

148
00:10:54,609 --> 00:10:55,598
<i>After all...</i>

149
00:10:56,611 --> 00:10:58,238
<i>without power...</i>

150
00:10:58,914 --> 00:11:00,575
<i>I can't do anything!</i>

151
00:11:02,818 --> 00:11:08,017
<i>Because I had no power...</i>
<i>Everyone was killed!</i>

152
00:11:11,093 --> 00:11:14,187
<i>No...</i>
<i>You let them be killed.</i>

153
00:11:16,365 --> 00:11:19,493
<i>You only...watched.</i>

154
00:11:20,769 --> 00:11:22,259
<i>If only I had power...</i>

155
00:11:23,939 --> 00:11:25,497
<i>If only I had power...</i>

156
00:11:36,785 --> 00:11:39,253
Sasuke! You're awake...
Huh?!

157
00:11:42,657 --> 00:11:43,487
Huh?

158
00:11:48,964 --> 00:11:49,931
That's...

159
00:11:50,866 --> 00:11:51,833
Sasuke?

160
00:12:07,616 --> 00:12:08,514
Sakura...

161
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,141
Sakura...

162
00:12:31,914 --> 00:12:34,576
Who did this to you?

163
00:12:36,185 --> 00:12:37,379
Who is it?

164
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:41,187
<i>The Curse Marks run</i>
<i>around his entire body?!</i>

165
00:12:42,424 --> 00:12:45,257
Sasuke...
That body?

166
00:12:59,341 --> 00:13:00,205
Don't worry.

167
00:13:00,576 --> 00:13:03,841
On the contrary,
strength is rapidly flowing in...

168
00:13:05,147 --> 00:13:06,512
Right now I feel good.

169
00:13:07,883 --> 00:13:09,316
That guy gave this to me.

170
00:13:09,785 --> 00:13:10,376
Huh?

171
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,054
At last I understand...

172
00:13:14,256 --> 00:13:15,848
I'm an Avenger...

173
00:13:16,792 --> 00:13:19,522
On my road, I must put power
into my hands...

174
00:13:20,029 --> 00:13:22,759
even if it means abandoning
myself to the devil.

175
00:13:28,404 --> 00:13:30,838
<i>So...I see...</i>

176
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:34,867
<i>So the mark on the neck</i>
<i>that this girl called Sakura spoke of</i>

177
00:13:34,944 --> 00:13:37,105
<i>is this Curse Mark.</i>

178
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:39,004
<i>But...</i>

179
00:13:39,381 --> 00:13:41,679
<i>I didn't think he could stand up...</i>

180
00:13:42,284 --> 00:13:44,184
Sakura, tell me...

181
00:13:44,453 --> 00:13:46,887
Who harmed you?

182
00:13:47,857 --> 00:13:48,789
Me!

183
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:55,255
Huh?

184
00:13:55,331 --> 00:13:56,263
Ino!

185
00:13:57,032 --> 00:13:58,795
If you stay like that
you're gonna get involved!

186
00:13:58,968 --> 00:14:00,595
Come back to this body!

187
00:14:01,036 --> 00:14:03,095
Choji, you too,
come over here and hide.

188
00:14:03,239 --> 00:14:04,536
Y-Yeah.

189
00:14:05,007 --> 00:14:06,167
Uh oh.

190
00:14:06,775 --> 00:14:07,901
Release!

191
00:14:10,746 --> 00:14:12,475
Okay, she's back!

192
00:14:12,681 --> 00:14:13,841
Shikamaru!

193
00:14:13,916 --> 00:14:16,316
What's going to happen now?

194
00:14:16,385 --> 00:14:17,852
How should I know?

195
00:14:31,934 --> 00:14:33,196
Wha?!

196
00:14:33,269 --> 00:14:35,760
W-What's this?

197
00:14:44,079 --> 00:14:45,569
<i>No matter...</i>

198
00:14:46,782 --> 00:14:48,113
<i>how you look at it...</i>

199
00:14:49,652 --> 00:14:50,778
<i>his Chakras are...</i>

200
00:14:51,921 --> 00:14:53,115
<i>too big!</i>

201
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:57,553
Dosu, this half dead bastard
is nothing to be scared of!

202
00:14:58,093 --> 00:15:00,220
Stop, Zaku! Don't you understand?!

203
00:15:00,896 --> 00:15:03,194
I'll take care of all of them...

204
00:15:03,666 --> 00:15:05,099
in one fell swoop!

205
00:15:06,201 --> 00:15:07,896
Super Sonic Slicing Wave!

206
00:15:25,054 --> 00:15:27,420
Heh! He must have been blown to pieces.

207
00:15:27,556 --> 00:15:28,853
- Who did?
- Huh?!

208
00:15:33,429 --> 00:15:34,293
Zaku!

209
00:15:38,467 --> 00:15:39,195
<i>He's fast!</i>

210
00:15:39,601 --> 00:15:42,968
<i>Moreover, he took in those two,</i>
<i>and in the blink of an eye.</i>

211
00:15:46,275 --> 00:15:47,207
Fire Style!

212
00:15:47,276 --> 00:15:48,504
Phoenix Flower Jutsu!

213
00:15:49,578 --> 00:15:50,476
Don't push your luck!

214
00:15:50,546 --> 00:15:52,104
I'll blow them off!

215
00:15:54,149 --> 00:15:54,843
What?!

216
00:15:55,751 --> 00:15:56,945
Shuriken's in the fire?!

217
00:15:59,421 --> 00:16:00,786
Zaku, below you!

218
00:16:11,967 --> 00:16:14,060
<i>The quality of the Chakra</i>
<i>is completely different...</i>

219
00:16:15,304 --> 00:16:17,135
<i>Is that really Sasuke?</i>

220
00:16:17,773 --> 00:16:19,968
<i>What happened?</i>
<i>What in the world...?</i>

221
00:16:23,612 --> 00:16:25,546
It seems like you're
proud of your arms...

222
00:16:26,081 --> 00:16:26,775
You!

223
00:16:29,585 --> 00:16:31,644
S-Stop it!

224
00:16:35,190 --> 00:16:38,751
<i>Sasuke will definitely come for me.</i>

225
00:17:01,517 --> 00:17:03,712
You're the only one left.

226
00:17:05,454 --> 00:17:06,614
You...

227
00:17:06,688 --> 00:17:08,952
make it a little more fun for me.

228
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:18,764
<i>This isn't...</i>

229
00:17:25,474 --> 00:17:26,498
<i>This isn't...</i>

230
00:17:32,614 --> 00:17:33,774
<i>This is not like...</i>

231
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:36,317
<i>Sasuke!</i>

232
00:17:43,692 --> 00:17:45,956
S-Stop!!

233
00:17:50,199 --> 00:17:51,223
Stop it.

234
00:18:01,743 --> 00:18:02,767
Please...

235
00:18:06,482 --> 00:18:07,380
Stop.

236
00:18:26,935 --> 00:18:28,835
<i>The Curse Mark is withdrawing...</i>

237
00:18:29,404 --> 00:18:31,235
<i>We're saved for now.</i>

238
00:18:32,174 --> 00:18:32,970
Sasuke!

239
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,580
You're strong.

240
00:18:43,619 --> 00:18:48,818
Sasuke... We can't defeat you
the way you are now.

241
00:18:50,826 --> 00:18:52,384
This is our fee for settling this...

242
00:18:52,861 --> 00:18:55,091
Please let us withdraw from here.

243
00:18:55,264 --> 00:18:55,992
Huh?

244
00:19:02,304 --> 00:19:07,742
It seems selfish, but we now have
something we need to confirm, too.

245
00:19:09,711 --> 00:19:12,305
That being said,
let's make a promise.

246
00:19:12,414 --> 00:19:16,578
If there's another opportunity to
battle with you in this test,

247
00:19:17,085 --> 00:19:19,610
we won't run or hide.

248
00:19:26,061 --> 00:19:27,187
Wait!

249
00:19:28,931 --> 00:19:31,263
Who in the world is Orochimaru?

250
00:19:31,333 --> 00:19:33,130
What did he do to Sasuke?!

251
00:19:33,435 --> 00:19:35,027
Why Sasuke?!

252
00:19:36,738 --> 00:19:37,932
I don't know...

253
00:19:38,473 --> 00:19:42,773
We were just given orders to
make the hit on Sasuke.

254
00:19:45,747 --> 00:19:49,410
<i>Though you ordered us to</i>
<i>assassinate Sasuke,</i>

255
00:19:49,551 --> 00:19:52,384
<i>you got to him first.</i>

256
00:19:53,455 --> 00:19:57,516
<i>Moreover, you didn't kill him,</i>
<i>and left that Curse Mark instead.</i>

257
00:19:58,327 --> 00:20:00,352
<i>I don't know what you're thinking...</i>

258
00:20:12,307 --> 00:20:13,797
Hey! Are you okay?!

259
00:20:14,176 --> 00:20:16,804
It's a pain, but Ino,
I'll leave Lee to you.

260
00:20:16,878 --> 00:20:17,537
Got it.

261
00:20:18,747 --> 00:20:21,113
<i>That Chakra...</i>
<i>It's abnormal.</i>

262
00:20:21,984 --> 00:20:25,784
<i>The Uchiha clan...</i>
<i>this good, huh?</i>

263
00:20:27,522 --> 00:20:29,922
Sakura's in danger!

264
00:20:30,092 --> 00:20:33,994
It's okay...
I'll protect Sakura.

265
00:20:34,463 --> 00:20:36,693
Well, what should we do
with this guy?

266
00:20:36,999 --> 00:20:38,091
Kick him awake?

267
00:20:38,166 --> 00:20:39,929
Can I do it?

268
00:20:44,606 --> 00:20:46,369
What am I?

269
00:20:50,879 --> 00:20:52,039
<i>Sasuke...</i>

270
00:21:05,355 --> 00:21:09,815
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

271
00:21:09,893 --> 00:21:18,164
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

272
00:21:19,236 --> 00:21:27,905
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

273
00:21:28,345 --> 00:21:36,218
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

274
00:21:37,554 --> 00:21:42,787
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

275
00:21:42,859 --> 00:21:46,989
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

276
00:21:47,063 --> 00:21:50,624
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

277
00:21:50,934 --> 00:21:59,501
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

278
00:21:59,776 --> 00:22:04,839
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

279
00:22:04,915 --> 00:22:09,318
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

280
00:22:09,519 --> 00:22:13,285
<i>Just sing.</i>

281
00:22:13,456 --> 00:22:18,689
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

282
00:22:18,829 --> 00:22:20,956
<i>The two are one</i>

283
00:22:21,064 --> 00:22:27,333
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

284
00:22:27,838 --> 00:22:32,935
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

285
00:22:37,867 --> 00:22:39,300
Hey, what's up Akamaru?

286
00:22:39,368 --> 00:22:41,461
Wait a minute, Naruto,
he's acting strange.

287
00:22:42,671 --> 00:22:43,729
What, are you hungry?

288
00:22:44,306 --> 00:22:46,501
Doesn't seem like it.
How about a walk?

289
00:22:47,042 --> 00:22:50,011
I know. You're looking for
an electric pole, aren't you?

290
00:22:52,581 --> 00:22:54,139
He bit me!

291
00:22:54,783 --> 00:22:58,310
Next pisode: "Akamaru Trembles:
Gaara's Cruel Strength!

292
00:22:58,654 --> 00:23:01,555
What in the world do
you want, anyway?
